# 7. もうひとりの自分の分も

Miku: Huh? I'm back in my own SEKAI...?
Miku: Where's me-but-not-me?
Miku: Heeey!
Miku: She's gone...
Miku: But I wanted to talk to her more... Does this mean I'm never gonna see her again?
Miku: Still...
???: Is something the matter, Miku?
Miku: Oh...!
Miku: KAITO, you gotta hear this!
Miku: You won't believe it! That voice I heard before was Miku!
KAITO: That voice you heard...?
Miku: Yeah, the one that said, “You can do it!” It was me, but not me, and she was trying to cheer for me and for all of us!
KAITO: H-Hang on... Take a deep breath for me first. Then, say what you just said a little more slowly.
Miku: Sure!
Miku: Breathe in... Breathe out...
KAITO: Interesting... And you met a different Miku in this strange SEKAI?
Miku: Yup! Me-but-not-me said our shows give her lots of encouragement every time she watches!
Miku: She also said how Tsukasa and the others are gonna be just fine as long as we keep trying our best for them!
Miku: And she wished us luck in the end.
KAITO: I see...
KAITO: Then, we'll also need to do our best to not disappoint her.
Miku: Yeah! Our show's gonna be so amazing☆
Miku: So, let's go!
KAITO: I still can't believe what happened. To think that I'd meet another me...
KAITO: (I thought we were the only ones watching over Vivid BAD SQUAD from a SEKAI until now.)
KAITO: But to find out that there are others watching over us...
KAITO: I can't help but feel encouraged!
Luka: Huh? KAITO, what are you doing here?
Luka: Len and the others have been looking all over for you. They're mad about you not helping them get ready for our event!
KAITO: What?! It wasn't on purpose.
Luka: Really? Then, care to explain?
KAITO: So...
Miku: Wait, Luka, you met a different Luka?
Luka: Yes, and guess what she said.
Luka: She thanked us for always supporting the girls and said she hopes that we'll keep doing our best since all they can do is watch over them.
Rin: She did...?!
Len: That means this other you also wants what's best for Minori and the others.
Luka: She does. She may even be watching over us and this SEKAI right now.
KAITO: Wow...!
KAITO: Then, we have to make our show the best we've ever done! To give hope not just to Minori and the others, but to this other Luka as well!
MEIKO: I agree! Which means we'll have to practice quite a lot to make that happen!
Luka: Yes, let's do our best!
Len: ♪————! ♪————!!
Rin: Whoooaaa! Len's totally energized!
KAITO: He is... Something good must've happened.
Rin: Like what?! Oh, maybe he won some free ice cream or something!
Miku: Only you and KAITO would be jumping for joy over that, Rin.
Luka: Still, I think our show's going to be quite a good one.
Rin: ♪————...
???: That was nice.
Rin: Oh...
Rin: MEIKO...
MEIKO: I can tell from the way you're singing...
MEIKO: You want them to feel your kindness. You want to be there for them.
Rin: Yeah, for Mafuyu's sake. For all their sakes...
Rin: Also, I'm singing on behalf of the other me watching over me.
MEIKO: I see...
Rin: *Nod*
Rin: ♪————
Rin: ♪———— ♪————...
MEIKO: ♪—— ♪————
Rin & MEIKO: ♪———— ♪————...
